Package: noaar
Title: Create Maps And Time Series Plots Of Earthquakes Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Hugo", "Nomanyon", , "hugostar84@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package offers tools to create time series plots
  and maps of earthquakes data with specific columns. The functions
  eq_clean_data() and eq_location_clean() can be used to clean
  the data and create the columns necessary(DATE, COUNTRY,
  LOCATION_NAME) for our data analysis. The function
  geom_timeline() creates time series plots which can be
  annotated with geom_timeline_label(). The function
  eq_create_label() helps create popups on interactive maps
  created using eq_map().
